text: Jab Mila Tu () is an Indian Hindi-language drama television series which aired on JioCinema from 22 January 2024 to 26 February 2024. The series stars Mohsin Khan, Eisha Singh, Pratik Sehajpal and Alisha Chopra. == Cast == * Mohsin Khan as Maddy * Eisha Singh as Aneri * Pratik Sehajpal as Jigar * Alisha Chopra as Mint == Production == The series was announced on JioCinema. Principal photography of the series wrapped in December 2023. == Music == == Reception == A critic writing for Times Now gave the series out of 5 stars. Arpita Mondal of Midgard Times awarded the series six-and-a-half out of ten stars. == References == == Other websites == * * Jab Mila Tu on JioCinema Category:2024 Indian television series debuts Category:2020s Indian television series Category:2020s drama television series
